name: Trivia Crack World Legacy
summary: Welcome to Trivia Crack World Legacy, the first immersive trivia experience on Meta Quest! Join Willy, your friendly host, and his six friends who are experts in different fields: Tina (art), Héctor (history), Pop (entertainment), Bonzo (sports), Albert (science), and Tito (geography). They will challenge you with thousands of questions that will test your knowledge. In the park, you can meet them, interact with them, and take photos.
